These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy, iris, lily
There 4 different types of food: grapes, grapefruit, garlic, orange
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, december, may
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, iced-tea, juice
City: hannover, liverpool, paris, venice
 1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 4. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating orange is the person eating orange##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
10. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person eating orange##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person eating garlic and the person who's birthday is in february##2
13. the person who growsiris is the person traveling to venice##1
14. the person traveling to paris is the person who growspoppy##1
15. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Flower           | dahlia | iris | lily  | poppy    |
| Food   | grapefruit     | orange   | garlic  | grapes  |
| Birthday           | february        | december    | may        | october |
| Beverage         | juice    | mirinda      | water   | iced-tea    |
| City     | hannover  | venice     | liverpool | paris |

