.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, librarian, doctor, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, may, july
There 4 different types of food: potato, grapes, pomegranate, asparagus
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, alhambra, tiparillo, pall-mall
House: cape-cod, townhouse, cottage, ranch-style
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 2. the librarian is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 3. the teacher is in an odd position##4
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the cottage house##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is the townhouse house##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
 7. the social-worker is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the ranch-style house##1
11. the doctor is on the far left##1
12. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person eating potato##1
13. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Job      | doctor        | social-worker       | teacher    | librarian       |
| Birthday         | may | march      | july | december |
| Food   | asparagus     | pomegranate | grapes  | potato   |
| Cigar   | alhambra   | pall-mall         | siglo   | tiparillo      |
| House         | townhouse      | cape-cod     | cottage    | ranch-style      |

