.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, dancing, puzzles
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, cat, hamster
4 different games are played: chess, monopoly, poker, canasta
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, balloon-flower, bellflower
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, aquamarine, ebony, ivory
 1. the person who growsmarigold is the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 8. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
12. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
14. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby          | dancing | fishing | drawing     | puzzles |
| Pet           | cat  | hamster   | fish | frog  |
| Game   | poker  | canasta      | monopoly     | chess   |
| Flower         | bellflower | lily  | marigold   | balloon-flower    |
| Color     | ebony | aquamarine    | ivory     | blue |

