.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, weightlifting, volleyball
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, tulip, bellflower, aconite
House: farmhouse, futuristic, colonial, tower
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, bridge, whist
City: london, hamburg, boston, hannover
 1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the colonial house is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 4. the tower house is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to boston##2
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 8. the person playing canasta is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
10. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who growsaconite##1
13. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
14. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
15. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Sport         | volleyball | skiing    | badminton | weightlifting       |
