 2. the colombian is in an even position##4
 3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the colombian##1
 4. the canadian is in an even position##4
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 8. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 9. the indonesian is the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking cola is the person traveling to prague##1
11. the indonesian is the person traveling to marseilles##1
12. the person driving the tram is the person traveling to colone##1
13. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
14. the person drinking cola is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
