 9. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the fish is the person who growslily##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
12. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
14. the person playing monopoly is between the owner of the fish and the fan of funk##2

