 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 9. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
10. the person playing whist is between the architect and the person watching disaster movies##2
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
12. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating kale##1
13. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
14. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero | mystery  | time-travel | disaster  |
| Job   | teacher     | architect    | journalist     | doctor      |
| Birthday   | september  | may  | august     | february |
| Food           | spinach      | potato | kale       | cauliflower     |
| Game     | canasta      | scrabble | whist  | billiard   |

